Instructions for compiling Cli Calc from source code

Requirements (tested on):
	- libmpfr 3 or newer
	- libgmp 3 or newer
	- g++ 4.4.3 or newer
	- make 3.8 or newer

For Debian:
	- sudo apt-get install build-essential libgmp3-dev libmpfr-dev make

Install:
	- make
	- make install
	(might require administrator privileges)

Uninstall:
	- make uninstall
	(might require administrator privileges)
